content:
Results

  • Interaction between learning task and logical form is significant at .01

      F(1, 84) = 22.07

  • Alpha: Conjunction easier to learn than disjunction (18.0 vs. 30.8)

  • Inflate: Conjunction is harder to learn than disjunction (29.1 vs. 9.4)

  • Inflate disjunction is easier than Alpha disjunction (9.4 vs. 30.8)


  • Specific causal knowledge increases rate of learning.
